  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Establishment  Management of Humanitarian Hubs and Common Services in North Eastern Nigeria</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Through this twelve-month project, IOM will contribute to ensuring an adequate humanitarian response to the needs of IDPs and host communities in North Eastern Nigeria. Through the establishment of Humanitarian Hubs (HH), IOM&#x2019;s proposed action will provide humanitarian partners working in Maiduguri with a stronger logistical base and greater access in the North East.   This will expand the reach of activities to provide affected populations with live-saving services, including the activities IOM is currently carrying out.</narrative>
  </description>
